    APIGW ==>|HTTP + JWT| BS
    APIGW ==>|HTTP + JWT| NS

    BS -.->|gRPC :50051| US
    BS -.->|gRPC :50052| RS
    NS -.->|gRPC :50051| US
    RS -.->|gRPC :50051| US

    BS -->|Publish Events| RMQ
    RMQ -->|Consume Events| NS

    RS <-->|Cache Read/Write| Redis

    US <-->|Entity Framework Core| DB1
    RS <-->|EF Core + Spatial Types| DB2
    BS <-->|Entity Framework Core| DB3
    NS <-->|Entity Framework Core| DB4

